Maintainer: Marlyne Meijerink-Bosman <m.l.meijerink@tilburguniversity.edu>
Description: This package allows researchers to compute a range of exogenous 
    and endogenous statistics for relational event modeling. Statistics are 
    collected in an array compatible for estimation of a relational event model 
    with relevent::rem. 
